snippet.title: Endless Memories - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore a magical world of dreams in this epic 2D action-adventure #metroidvania that mixes a handcrafted non-linear world with ARPG elements.

Endless Memories comes to PC on October 19th!

Wishlist on Steam: http://bit.ly/SteamEndlessMemories
